modName: Succubus Preset for ECE and Racemenu
summary: Not my creation, I only converted ECE file to Racemenu.

내가 만든거 아님 ㅋ.ㅋ

[b][color=#ead1dc][size=3]Description[/size][/color][/b]
Here's a beautiful and adorable character preset, I named her Leah, but the original creator actually named her Succubus. :P


For Enhanced Character Edit Users,
put the cme to the following directory : Documents\my games\skyrim\CME_save.

For Racemenu Users,
put the jsot to the following directory : Data\skse\plugins\CharGen\Presets.


Character creation is not my work :P 
All I did was converting ECE to racemenu.
A user named, 44 made it.
